cs.HC, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.CC, cs.CE

The paper focuses on examining the factors affecting the adoption of 3G services among Indian people, which involves the study of human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and social and information networks (cs.SI). The study also collects data from various sources and analyzes it using MS Excel and MATLAB, which falls under the category of computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE). The paper also discusses the revised Technology Acceptance Model, which is related to the field of cybernetics (cs.CY) and computer communications (cs.CC).
